description: CD reissue. Barry White's Can't Get Enough is an iconic music album that has stood the test of time since it's release in 1974. This masterpiece features the smooth, soulful voice of the legendary Barry White, accompanied by a full orchestra and his signature deep bass lines. The album comprises of seven tracks, each showcasing Barry's unparalleled talent as a singer, songwriter, and producer. Notable tracks include "You're the First, the Last, My Everything," a timeless love song, "I Can't Believe You Love Me," a beautiful and emotional ballad, and "Can't Get Enough of Your Love, Babe," a groovy track with a catchy chorus. Overall, Can't Get Enough is a must-have for any music lover who appreciates soulful, timeless music that stands the test of time.
